---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import PageHero from '../../components/PageHero.astro';
import ImageText from '../../components/ImageText.astro';
import BookingCTA from '../../components/BookingCTA.astro';
---
<Layout
	title="People with Neurological Conditions"
	description="Specialist neurological rehabilitation in Clapham for MS, stroke, Parkinson's, cerebral palsy and other pathologies. Anti-gravity treadmill, hydrotherapy, Vojta therapy and psychological wellbeing support under one roof."
>
	<PageHero
		title="with Neurological Conditions"
		highlight="People"
		subtitle="The right rehabilitation, delivered consistently by the right people, makes a profound difference."
		breadcrumb="Neurological Conditions"
	/>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Specialist support"
		heading="Rehab that reaches every"
		highlight="corner of life"
		image="/neuro-rehab.jpg"
		imageAlt="Neurological rehabilitation at Balance Physio"
	>
		<p>Living with a neurological condition affects movement, balance, coordination, strength and independence in ways that reach into every area of daily life. The right rehabilitation, delivered consistently by the right people, makes a profound difference.</p>
		<p>At Balance, our specialist team supports people living with MS, stroke, Parkinson's, cerebral palsy and a wide range of other neurological pathologies.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Outside the treatment room"
		heading="Where the real progress"
		highlight="happens"
		reverse
		altBg
		image="/antigravity.webp"
		imageAlt="Anti-gravity treadmill at Balance Physio"
	>
		<p>Meaningful progress happens outside the treatment room, through consistent, active engagement with your programme. Our gym, movement studios and hydrotherapy facilities provide the environment for that daily work.</p>
		<p>Our anti-gravity treadmill enables safe, effective gait rehabilitation that rebuilds neural pathways and restores function in ways conventional therapy cannot always achieve.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Vojta therapy"
		heading="A specialist"
		highlight="neurophysiological approach"
		image="/vojta.jpg"
		imageAlt="Vojta therapy at Balance Physio"
	>
		<p>Vojta therapy is a specialist neurophysiological approach that activates the body's innate movement patterns and is a key part of our offer. It reflects the depth of expertise within our team and is one of the more specialised therapies available in London.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<ImageText
		eyebrow="Whole-person care"
		heading="Physical and"
		highlight="emotional support"
		reverse
		altBg
		image="/psychological-wellness.jpg"
		imageAlt="Psychological wellbeing support at Balance Physio"
	>
		<p>Neurological rehabilitation is emotionally demanding. Our psychological wellbeing support sits alongside physical rehabilitation, ensuring the whole person is cared for throughout what is often a long and complex journey.</p>
		<p>At Balance, we are committed to helping you restore function, independence and energy for life.</p>
	</ImageText>

	<BookingCTA />
</Layout>
